<title>MY FAITH LOOKS UP TO THEE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ginna'n ka hun en to,
 Kalvari Belam No;
 Lal Hukdampa,
 Ka pauchamna ngaiin;
 Ka gitloh lamang in,
 Tuni apat kei Nanga
 Hi tang ka.

[V2]
 2. Ka lunggil sawlsam hi,
 Lungsietna'n hihhat in;
 Ei hih taiman,
 Kei di'n na thih ziekin;
 Ka hun hehpihna chuh,
 Thiengtho, lum leh danglo;
 Mei bang kuong hen.

[V3]
 3. Damsung, lungkham buoina,
 Laka ka len laiin;
 Ei Puipa hin
 Thimna vak suoh sakin;
 Dah luonthi thiek hulin,
 Na kawm apat ka vak -
 Mang ding phal kin.

[V4]
 4. Ka hinkhuo a beih a,
 Thihna luipi vawt chun;
 Ei chup tieng leh,
 Lungsiet-in Hukdampa;
 Lauh ginlah lamang in,
 Tatsa chenna chunggam-
 Ah ei tunin.</lyrics>
</song>